VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(?:for|while)\s*\([^)]*(?:<|<=|>|>=)[^)]*(?:size|length|count|index|idx|i|j|k)[^)]*\)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:size\(\)|length\(\)|\.end\(\)|bounds|assert|sizeof\s*\(.*\)/sizeof
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects loops iterating over arrays, vectors, or strings.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Unsafe Loop Handling Over Arrays or Vectors.
